  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a first person horror decryption game, where players take on the role of a good friend of an alien cat who has been captured by an axe maniac. Players need to face puzzles that arise, rescue four good friends of the alien cat, collect fragmented information to advance the plot, and uncover the truth behind hidden and bizarre events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/5bf5943ade0951f3824b454f6015fe25.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were awakened by a ringing phone call in the middle of the night. After connecting, your friend asked you to save his buddy. You feel very strange...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.mp4?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have a 'special' friend! Everything in the house became very strange. I am fortunate that I did not become two-dimensional.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/1cd40f141f1604748158fb7a6241e629.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/1cd40f141f1604748158fb7a6241e629.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special physical interaction, volume audio, and PS1 style graphics environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.mp4?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a first person horror decryption game, where players take on the role of a good friend of an alien cat who has been captured by an axe maniac. Players need to face puzzles that arise, rescue four good friends of the alien cat, collect fragmented information to advance the plot, and uncover the truth behind hidden and bizarre events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/5bf5943ade0951f3824b454f6015fe25.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were awakened by a ringing phone call in the middle of the night. After connecting, your friend asked you to save his buddy. You feel very strange...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/4294224702c39fdf33cc55f59e284ddf.mp4?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I have a 'special' friend! Everything in the house became very strange. I am fortunate that I did not become two-dimensional.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/1cd40f141f1604748158fb7a6241e629.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/1cd40f141f1604748158fb7a6241e629.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special physical interaction, volume audio, and PS1 style graphics environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.poster.avif?t=1754221393\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.webm?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3426330/extras/01e7ceb016b0814288bbed638e433e24.mp4?t=1754221393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
